E4Plus1.uk.description: G.I. (Annoyed Grunt): Homer accidentally signs up for basic training in the army. And Marge and Grampa get roped in when they try to get him released. (S18 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ice Cream of Margie (With the Light Blue Hair): Marge, feeling overshadowed by Homer's new career selling ice cream, starts creating ice lolly stick sculptures. (S18 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: E My Sports: When Bart starts earning money from video game competitions, Homer becomes his coach, and their team make it to the finals in South Korea. (S30 Ep17/23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Bart's Birthday: Bart has to organise his own birthday party when Homer forgets to post the invitations. Mr Burns fakes his own death. (S36 Ep1/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - The Yellow Lotus: The Simpsons stumble across a mystery and an old enemy while they're on holiday at a peculiar island resort. Dr Hibbert drugs an otter. (S36 Ep2/18)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox for Stand...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Up To Cancer: Celebrities join the Gogglebox regulars to react to our top telly in this special episode for Stand Up To Cancer. (S24 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Free Guy
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2021) Comedy action starring Ryan Reynolds. Guy lives in Free City. Free City isn't real. Nor is Guy. It's all a big online game. Can he take down the corrupt game publisher?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pansexual Sarah can't wait to road test her new body on her first date as a woman. Plumber Jamie's love life has gone down the u-bend, so he's all cisterns go to find a partner. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pansexual sex therapist Mariia's after a not-so-average Mr or Mrs who's not too tired for sex. Old romantic at heart Alannah seeks a forever fella who can speak her love language. (S11 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox for Stand...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Up To Cancer: Celebrities join the Gogglebox regulars to react to our top telly in this special episode for Stand Up To Cancer. (S24 Ep7) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pansexual Sarah can't wait to road test her new body on her first date as a woman. Plumber Jamie's love life has gone down the u-bend, so he's all cisterns go to find a partner. (S11 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: Big Baby Ball: When Coach Mellor singles out Adam during dodgeball, Beverly intervenes and gets him fired. But then Murray and Adam see Mellor in a new light. (S2 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Goldbergs
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Goldberg Thanksgiving: Beverly challenges Erica to participate in Jazzercise after Erica says her mum's obsession is sad. Marvin visits the family at Thanksgiving. (S2 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Don't Tell the Bride
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sonny is a party fanatic. How will his bride Jazmin greet his plans for a zoo-themed Ibizan beach party wedding with everyone covered in animal-print body paint?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Lego Masters Australia
E4Plus1.uk.description: City in the Sky: Previous winners and finalists return for a Grand Masters special series. First up, they must create a world suspended high in the sky. (S5 Ep1) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Da Mimmo: Gordon tries to transform New Jersey Italian restaurant Da Mimmo, which is run by a mother and her three sons - two of whom see the business as a failure... (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Juicy Box: Gordon helps a Haitian juice bar and restaurant in Brooklyn. Jacques opened the Juicy Box to provide healthier options for the neighbourhood, but it's fallen into chaos. (S8 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Playing with Fire
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Fun-filled family comedy starring John Cena. A macho fireman has to babysit three impish kids after saving them from a blaze in the remote California woodlands.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Secret Headquarters
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2022) Family comedy with Michael Pea. A young lad discovers that his slacker dad is a superhero. And before he's got used to the idea, he must foil a villain's plot to bring his dad down.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Great New Year Bake Off
E4Plus1.uk.description: As the oven timers strike midnight, teams of legendary bakers from seasons gone by bring in 2026 the only way they know how... with fabulous festive baking and plenty of merry making. [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: You Only Move Twice: Homer is offered a new job by mysterious businessman Hank Scorpio. But will Marge, Bart and Lisa be happy in their idyllic new home town? (S8 Ep2/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hurricane Neddy: The Flanders' home is blown down by a hurricane and the Leftorium is looted. Homer leads the rebuilding project, but will Ned be happy with his new house? (S8 Ep8/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Springfield Files: Homer thinks he's seen an alien in the woods. This could be a case for Mulder and Scully (guest stars David Duchovny and Gillian Anderson). (S8 Ep10/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Aladdin
E4Plus1.uk.description: (2019) Guy Ritchie's vigorously lamp-rubbing musical remake of the Disney classic, starring Will Smith as the genie. Can urchin Aladdin raise himself up and capture the princess's heart?

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer's Phobia: Homer's prejudices surface when Bart befriends a gay shop owner (guest star John Waters). So he decides to take Bart hunting - but it doesn't go to plan. (S8 Ep15/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer vs the Eighteenth Amendment: When alcohol is banned in Springfield, Moe's Tavern becomes a speakeasy and Homer re-invents himself as the Beer Baron. (S8 Ep18/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Canine Mutiny: Bart buys Laddie, an amazing new dog, with a credit card that's accidentally been sent to Santa's Little Helper. (S8 Ep20/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Old Man and the Lisa: Mr Burns loses all his money and employs Lisa to help him earn back his fortune. But they don't see eye to eye over ethical issues. (S8 Ep21/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer and Apu: When Apu loses the Kwik-E-Mart, he moves in with the Simpsons. And then Homer joins him on a pilgrimage to the first ever Kwik-E-Mart, in the Himalayas. (S5 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Celebrity Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: Some of Britain's favourite personalities hit the sofa and tune in for The 1% Club, Spy in the Ocean, Fake Profile, The Yorkshire Vet and lots more great TV. (S5 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: The top TV includes: Strictly Come Dancing, Celebrity SAS: Who Dares Wins, A Very Royal Scandal, The Yorkshire Vet, This Morning (gurning) and My Mum, Your Dad. (S24 Ep3)

Film4.uk.title: The Equalizer
Film4.uk.description: (2014) Thriller. Denzel Washington stars as an ex-soldier who comes out of retirement to help a teenage sex worker who's been assaulted by her pimp.

Film4.uk.title: Withnail and I
Film4.uk.description: (1987) Richard E Grant and Paul McGann star in Bruce Robinson's cult comedy as hard-drinking, substance-abusing unemployed actors who flee to Cumbria to escape their squalid London life.

Film4.uk.title: Walking and Talking
Film4.uk.description: (1996) Comedy with Catherine Keener and Anne Heche. A successful woman's best friend is getting married - making her feel unlucky in love. But is everything as rosy as it at first seems?

Film4.uk.title: The Lady Eve
Film4.uk.description: (1941) Screwball romcom with Barbara Stanwyck and Henry Fonda. A con artist is forced to change tack when she falls for her mark and he dumps her for trying to con him in the first place.

Film4.uk.title: The Straight Story
Film4.uk.description: (1999) David Lynch's fact-based drama with Richard Farnsworth. Alvin Straight drives hundreds of miles across the USA on a lawnmower to visit his dying brother - Harry Dean Stanton.

Film4.uk.title: The Golden Voyage of Sinbad
Film4.uk.description: (1973) Can Sinbad stop a master magician from reaching the Fountain of Destiny on the lost land of Lemuria and being crowned the new leader of Marabia?

Film4.uk.title: Stormbreaker
Film4.uk.description: (2006) Family action-thriller with Alex Pettyfer and Mickey Rourke. British intelligence recruit a schoolboy to take on the man who killed his dad and is planning to unleash a deadly virus.

Film4.uk.title: The Day the Earth Stood Still
Film4.uk.description: (2008) Remake of the sci-fi classic with Keanu Reeves. An alien visits Earth to tell humankind to stop destroying the planet. But when he's attacked, he decides to eradicate us instead...

Film4.uk.title: Mission: Impossible - Dead...

Film4.uk.title: Late Night with the Devil
Film4.uk.description: (2023) Unsettling found-footage horror with David Dastmalchian. A has-been host tries to save his 70s talk show using a demonically possessed 13-year-old girl. Really, what could go wrong?

Film4.uk.title: Fantastic Voyage
Film4.uk.description: (1966) Classic sci-fi adventure. Raquel Welch and Donald Pleasence are among the crew of a miniaturised submarine that's injected into an injured diplomat's body in a bid to save his life.

Film4.uk.title: The Caine Mutiny

Film4.uk.title: The Frogmen
